Sagil Latin American Opportunities Fund Key Developments

Sagil Latin American Opportunities Fund Announces Board Changes
Jul 6 17
The Board of Directors of Sagil Latin American Opportunities Fund announced the resignation of Justin Berkeley Clarke from the Board, effective 30 June 2017. Mr. Andrew Linford has been appointed as a Director of the company effective 30 June 2017.


Sagil Latin American Opportunities Fund Announces the Change in Directors
Sep 17 15
The directors of Sagil Latin American Opportunities Fund announced that Mr. Desmond Ian Catterall has resigned as Director of the company with effect from September 15, 2015. Mr. Mark Hendricks has been appointed as a Director of the company, effective September 15, 2015. Mr. Hendricks is a founding partner of Sagil Capital LLP and is the CFO and COO. Mr. Hendricks is responsible for the finance and operational activities of the firm. Mr. Hendricks is also responsible for risk management and compliance and holds a seat on the investment committee.


