About Sagil Capital





Sagil Capital LLP was founded in August of 2008 to take advantage of investment opportunities in the growing financial markets of Latin America. Sagil is managed by a team of professionals with many years of investing experience in the region.The firm seeks to generate consistent attractive returns for our investors through in-depth fundamental research. Sagil has a strong culture of risk management with the foundations of our investment process being capital preservation and risk-adjusted returns. 
























Fund Overview





Sagil Capital is the investment advisor to the Sagil 
      Latin American Opportunities Fund. The Fund is a US dollar denominated long-short 
      equity fund seeking to generate attractive absolute returns in Latin America 
      across three investment strategies  arbitrage, relative value and 
      directional. In addition to companies listed in the region, the Fund also 
      invests in companies listed in other markets with significant exposure to 
      Latin America.





































 Sagil Capital LLP is authorised and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority.Sagil Capital LLP is registered as an Exempt Reporting Advisor with the SEC.Click here for regulatory disclosures. UK Stewardship Code, Complaints Policy. 








