Sagil Latin American Opportunities Fund LP  Financing
Sagil Latin American Opportunities Fund LP just submitted form D announcing  Indefinite financing.  This is a new filing. Sagil Latin American Opportunities Fund LP was able to sell $23,950,000. The total private offering amount was Indefinite. The financing was made by 11 investors. Minimal accepted investment was $100,000. The financing document was filed on 2009-12-24. Sagil Latin American Opportunities Fund LP is based in  C/O SAGIL GENERAL PARTNER LTD. UGLAND HOUSE, PO BOX 309 GRAND CAYMAN KY1-1104. The firm's business is Pooled Investment Fund. The form was signed by  Sagil General Partner Ltd. Sagil General Partner Ltd..





